                    <!-- put your links in here 
                    
                    titles are in bold, you can add icons in front of it.
                    to find more icons, go here: https://glenthemes.tumblr.com/icons/iconsax
                    
                    example:
                    <b><i class="iconsax" icon-name="ICON_NAME_HERE"></i> title name</b>
                    
                    every link is an a tag, example:
                    <a href="URL">name of link</a>
                    
                    if you want every link to start on a new line, write <br> after it.
                    if you want a line to separate blocks, write <hr> in between.
                    
                    -->
                
                    <b><i class="iconsax" icon-name="star"></i> main navigation</b>
                    <a href="/">link name</a>
                    <a href="/">link name</a>
                    <a href="/">link name</a>
                    <a href="/">link name</a>
                    <a href="/">link name</a>
                    <a href="/">link name</a>
                    
                    <hr>
                    
                    <b><i class="iconsax" icon-name="chevron-right"></i> something else</b>
                    <a href="/">link name</a>
                    <a href="/">link name</a>
                    <a href="/">link name</a>
                    <a href="/">link name</a>
                    <a href="/">link name</a>
                    <a href="/">link name</a>
                    
                </div>
                
                <div class="pop-left-about">
                    
                    <!-- text block
                    any basic html styling works in here
                    wrap the first letter in <u> tags to get the big letter -->
                    
                    <u>N</u>unc tempus congue libero ac ullamcorper. Morbi sit amet sapien dignissim, sodales felis eget, ultricies turpis. Cras quis quam ultricies, volutpat risus id, finibus tellus. Suspendisse potenti.
                    <br><br>
                    Cras finibus nulla et velit tempus dapibus. Nullam egestas turpis sit amet mi venenatis, a consectetur nulla volutpat. Quisque malesuada accumsan magna. Sed volutpat purus non ex vulputate lacinia. 
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    
